<i>"Song of the Sirenas: Part II." </i>

01:06.125 --> 01:07.458
<c.speaker>Princess Elena?!

01:09.125 --> 01:10.625
<c.speakerTop>Princess Elena!

01:10.625 --> 01:11.625
<c.speakerTop>Is she... ?

01:11.625 --> 01:13.583
<c.speakerTop>Alive. Barely.

01:13.583 --> 01:15.125
<c.speakerTop>Wait! Where
are you taking her?!

01:15.125 --> 01:16.500
<c.speakerTop>To the <i>milagras! </i>

01:16.500 --> 01:18.958
<c.speakerTop>[whinnies]
The <i>milagras?! </i>

01:18.958 --> 01:20.583
<c.speakerTop>You can't do that!

01:20.583 --> 01:21.833
<c.speakerTop>Marisa!

01:25.000 --> 01:26.000
<c.speaker>[grunting]

01:30.125 --> 01:32.166
<c.speaker>Marzel!
She's over there!

01:32.166 --> 01:34.458
<c.speaker>What are you doing?!
You're turning her
into a sirena?!

01:34.458 --> 01:36.875
<c.speaker>No! If I just
wrap her chest,

01:36.875 --> 01:39.208
<c.speaker>maybe she'll breathe,
but not turn.

01:39.208 --> 01:40.875
<c.speaker>That's a big maybe.

01:40.875 --> 01:42.458
<c.speaker>Are you forgetting
she set us up?!

01:42.458 --> 01:45.875
<c.speaker>Are you forgetting
she tried to save us? Twice?!

01:47.875 --> 01:49.375
<c.speaker>Please work. Please...

01:58.958 --> 01:59.958
<c.speaker>[gasp]

01:59.958 --> 02:01.625
<c.speaker>[coughs]

02:03.458 --> 02:04.500
<c.speaker>Marisa?

02:04.500 --> 02:06.291
<c.speaker>[sigh of relief]

02:06.291 --> 02:08.000
<c.speaker>Where are we?

02:15.125 --> 02:17.083
<c.speaker>But how am I--

02:17.083 --> 02:18.583
<c.speaker>The <i>milagra. </i>

02:18.583 --> 02:21.125
<c.speaker>It lets you breathe
underwater.

02:21.125 --> 02:22.750
<c.speaker>What are you even
doing down here?

02:22.750 --> 02:24.291
<c.speaker>I was attacked.

02:24.291 --> 02:26.166
<c.speaker>By who?

02:26.166 --> 02:28.958
<c.speaker>The sorceress
who killed my parents

02:28.958 --> 02:31.000
<c.speaker>and is trying
to take over my kingdom.

02:31.000 --> 02:33.166
<c.speaker>I have to go back.

02:33.166 --> 02:35.125
<c.speaker>Wait! Let us help you.

02:35.125 --> 02:36.000
<c.speaker>-What?!
-What?!

02:36.000 --> 02:38.083
<c.speaker>Marzel,
this is our chance

02:38.083 --> 02:40.125
<c.speaker>to prove to the humans
that the sirenas
have changed.

02:40.125 --> 02:42.125
<c.speaker>Papá will never go for it.

02:42.125 --> 02:44.000
<c.speaker>He has to.
Elena needs us.

02:44.000 --> 02:45.083
<c.speaker>Her whole kingdom does.

02:45.083 --> 02:46.833
<c.speaker>This isn't our fight.

02:46.833 --> 02:49.250
<c.speaker>It is now.
Come with me!

02:53.875 --> 02:55.583
<c.speaker>Ugh! I lost Victor.

02:55.583 --> 02:57.291
<c.speaker>Same with Carla.

02:57.291 --> 02:59.083
<c.speaker>It's like she just
vanished in the crowd.

02:59.083 --> 03:03.375
<c.speaker>Uh, guys. Where's
the princesa's float?

03:03.375 --> 03:05.625
<c.speaker>Spread out and search
all the side canals. Now!

03:11.125 --> 03:14.000
<c.speaker>I told you to stay away
from the humans.

03:14.000 --> 03:15.750
<c.speaker>But instead,
you bring one to Coronado!

03:15.750 --> 03:18.166
<c.speaker>And their princess at that.

03:20.000 --> 03:21.833
<c.speaker>This will surely lead
to retaliation.

03:21.833 --> 03:23.000
<c.speaker>Surely!

03:23.000 --> 03:25.458
<c.speaker>Retaliation?
For saving me?

03:25.458 --> 03:27.000
<c.speaker>They'll give you a medal.

03:27.000 --> 03:28.583
<c.speaker>And if sirenas
help defeat Shuriki,

03:28.583 --> 03:31.958
<c.speaker>then every human in Avalor
will see that you're our allies.

03:31.958 --> 03:33.083
<c.speaker>Our friends.

03:33.083 --> 03:35.166
<c.speaker>Humans will never
be our friends.

03:35.166 --> 03:36.500
<c.speaker>But, Papá!

03:36.500 --> 03:38.333
<c.speaker>You should know
better than anyone, Marisa.

03:38.333 --> 03:40.416
<c.speaker>After they
almost took you from us.

03:42.000 --> 03:44.333
<c.speaker>What are you
talking about?

03:44.333 --> 03:47.291
<c.speaker>She doesn't remember,
Pescoro.

03:47.291 --> 03:49.333
<c.speaker>Well, perhaps
it's time she did.

03:51.250 --> 03:54.250
<c.speaker>It had been years
since we stopped sinking
the humans ships,

03:54.250 --> 03:57.458
<c.speaker>and you, my darling,
wanted to see the shore.

03:57.458 --> 03:59.750
<c.speaker>[seagulls calling]

03:59.750 --> 04:02.000
<c.speaker>[giggling]

04:03.875 --> 04:07.083
<c.speaker>Marisita, don't get
too close to the shore!

04:07.083 --> 04:09.458
<c.speaker>[giggling]

04:09.458 --> 04:10.583
<c.speaker>-[calling]
-Oh!

04:13.000 --> 04:15.208
<c.speaker>-[gasps]
-How did she do that?

04:15.208 --> 04:17.416
<c.speaker>I don't know.

04:20.708 --> 04:22.458
<c.speaker>Mami! Papi! Look at me!

04:22.458 --> 04:24.500
<c.speaker>[giggles]

04:24.500 --> 04:26.000
<c.speaker>Whoops!

04:26.000 --> 04:27.875
<c.speaker>[laughing]

04:27.875 --> 04:29.458
<c.speaker>[man grunting]

04:29.458 --> 04:31.708
<c.speaker>-Come back, <i>mija!  </i>
-Marisa!

04:31.708 --> 04:34.083
<c.speaker>Hey, those sirenas
are trying to lure that girl!

04:34.083 --> 04:36.583
<c.speaker>-[giggling]
-I'll save her!

04:36.583 --> 04:38.000
<c.speaker>[giggling]

04:38.000 --> 04:39.416
<c.speaker>-Gotcha!
-Papi!

04:39.416 --> 04:40.708
<c.speaker>-[gasp]
<i>-Mija! </i>

04:40.708 --> 04:42.250
<c.speaker>[man grunts]

04:48.250 --> 04:52.208
<c.speaker>That day, I realized humans
will always despise us,

04:52.208 --> 04:56.000
<c.speaker>and I decreed
that sirenas must never
approach them again.

05:02.125 --> 05:05.583
<c.speaker>Oh, Papá. I understand.

05:05.583 --> 05:08.708
<c.speaker>But they didn't know
who I was or what I was.

05:08.708 --> 05:10.833
<c.speaker>And they didn't know
we're different now.

05:13.291 --> 05:16.166
<c.speaker>So perhaps
it's time they did.

05:17.708 --> 05:20.250
<c.speaker>Marisa's right.

05:20.250 --> 05:21.708
<c.speaker>You want to show
the human world

05:21.708 --> 05:24.125
<c.speaker>you're no longer
our enemies?

05:24.125 --> 05:25.875
<c.speaker>Now's your chance.

05:25.875 --> 05:27.458
<c.speaker>[music playing]

05:27.458 --> 05:29.958
<c.speaker><i>♪ Lend me your hand ♪ </i>

05:29.958 --> 05:32.000
<c.speaker><i>♪ Help with this plight ♪ </i>

05:32.000 --> 05:36.166
<c.speaker><i>♪ Together we can </i>
<i>rise up and fight ♪ </i>

05:36.166 --> 05:38.208
<c.speaker><i>♪ To show </i>
<i>that you've changed ♪ </i>

05:38.208 --> 05:40.166
<c.speaker><i>♪ You gotta be tough ♪ </i>

05:40.166 --> 05:43.750
<c.speaker><i>♪ 'Cause words </i>
<i>just aren't enough ♪ </i>

05:43.750 --> 05:47.708
<c.speaker><i>♪ Now's your chance ♪ </i>

05:47.708 --> 05:52.375
<c.speaker><i>♪ Now's your chance ♪ </i>

05:52.375 --> 05:56.708
<c.speaker><i>♪ Your chance to prove </i>
<i>you want peace ♪ </i>

05:56.708 --> 06:00.208
<c.speaker><i>♪ And make amends </i>
<i>for past deeds ♪ </i>

06:00.208 --> 06:04.458
<c.speaker><i>♪ And then they'll see ♪ </i>

06:04.458 --> 06:09.000
<c.speaker><i>♪ Your spirit's true ♪ </i>

06:09.000 --> 06:11.000
<c.speaker><i>♪ They'll want it too ♪ </i>

06:11.000 --> 06:13.375
<c.speaker><i>♪ It's all up to you ♪ </i>

06:13.375 --> 06:16.583
<c.speaker><i>♪ Now's your chance ♪ </i>

06:21.250 --> 06:23.083
<c.speaker>We should listen
to them, Pescoro.

06:23.083 --> 06:26.000
<c.speaker>This could
change everything.

06:26.000 --> 06:29.000
<c.speaker>[sighs] I'm afraid the gulf
between us is too wide.

06:29.000 --> 06:31.583
<c.speaker>At the end of the day,
we are of the sea,

06:31.583 --> 06:33.208
<c.speaker>and they are of the land.

06:33.208 --> 06:36.000
<c.speaker>And that will never change.

06:36.000 --> 06:39.000
<c.speaker>But even the sea
and the land meet at the shore.

06:39.000 --> 06:41.000
<c.speaker>We can bridge that gulf,
if we try.

06:41.000 --> 06:42.708
<c.speaker>I have made my decision.

06:42.708 --> 06:45.333
<c.speaker>We will not meddle
in the humans' affairs.

06:47.000 --> 06:49.208
<c.speaker>One day, we will heal
these wounds.

06:49.208 --> 06:52.625
<c.speaker>But today is not that day.

06:52.625 --> 06:55.125
<c.speaker>Escort the princess
back to her world.

06:55.125 --> 06:56.125
<c.speaker>[sighs]

