<c.speaker><i>♪ Here I will stand ♪ </i>

07:04.875 --> 07:07.166
<c.speaker><i>♪ Right by your side ♪ </i>

07:07.166 --> 07:09.125
<c.speaker><i>♪ Our dream of peace ♪ </i>

07:09.125 --> 07:11.083
<c.speaker><i>♪ Will be the guide ♪ </i>

07:11.083 --> 07:13.291
<c.speaker><i>♪ We'll show the whole world ♪ </i>

07:13.291 --> 07:15.458
<c.speaker><i>♪ From near and far ♪ </i>

07:15.458 --> 07:17.458
<c.speaker><i>♪ Who you really are ♪ </i>

