<c.speaker><i>♪ Now's our chance ♪ </i>

07:24.958 --> 07:27.125
<c.speaker><i>♪ Now's our chance ♪ </i>

07:27.125 --> 07:31.458
<c.speaker><i>♪ Our chance to prove </i>
<i>you want peace ♪ </i>

07:31.458 --> 07:35.250
<c.speaker><i>♪ And make amends </i>
<i>for past deeds ♪ </i>

07:35.250 --> 07:37.458
<c.speaker><i>♪ And they will see ♪ </i>

07:37.458 --> 07:39.333
<c.speaker><i>♪ They will see ♪ </i>

07:39.333 --> 07:44.208
<c.speaker><i>♪ Our spirit's true ♪ </i>

07:44.208 --> 07:45.500
<c.speaker><i>♪ It's me and you ♪ </i>

07:45.500 --> 07:50.083
<c.speaker><i>♪ It's up to us two ♪ </i>

07:51.958 --> 07:54.291
<c.speaker><i>♪ Now's our chance ♪ </i>

07:54.291 --> 07:56.458
<c.speaker><i>♪ Now's our chance ♪ </i>

07:56.458 --> 07:58.708
<c.speaker><i>♪ Now's our chance ♪ </i>

07:58.708 --> 08:00.625
<c.speaker><i>♪ Now's our chance ♪ </i>

08:00.625 --> 08:05.416
<c.speaker><i>♪ Now's our chance ♪ </i>

08:15.833 --> 08:19.958
<c.speaker>I got a strange feeling
she's gonna disobey
another order.

08:19.958 --> 08:21.875
<c.speaker>Not this time.
Because you and I

08:21.875 --> 08:24.208
<c.speaker>are going to stop her
before she can. Come on.

08:30.208 --> 08:32.000
<c.speaker>That parade
was so much fun!

08:32.000 --> 08:33.166
<c.speaker>I wish we could do it again!

08:33.166 --> 08:34.500
<c.speaker>Me, too, <i>mija. </i>

08:34.500 --> 08:36.458
<c.speaker>We all have
a lot to celebrate,

08:36.458 --> 08:37.500
<c.speaker>thanks to Elena.

08:37.500 --> 08:39.250
<c.speaker>Where is Elena?

08:39.250 --> 08:41.583
<c.speaker>I haven't seen her
since we boarded the floats.

08:41.583 --> 08:45.166
<c.speaker>She's probably
still out there enjoying
the adulation of her people.

08:45.166 --> 08:47.458
<c.speaker>I know that is
what I would be doing.

08:47.458 --> 08:49.375
<c.speaker>[rumbling]

08:54.083 --> 08:55.958
<c.speaker>-[gasp] Shuriki?!
-No!

08:55.958 --> 08:59.458
<c.speaker>The real Queen of Avalor
is back!

08:59.458 --> 09:01.583
<c.speaker>And since I'm
in such a good mood,

09:01.583 --> 09:05.083
<c.speaker>I'll simply lock you up
in the tower... for now.

09:09.500 --> 09:11.250
<c.speaker>This is
how we found the float.

09:11.250 --> 09:12.625
<c.speaker>And the Crown Princess?

09:12.625 --> 09:13.708
<c.speaker>Nowhere in sight.

09:13.708 --> 09:16.500
<c.speaker>Duke Cristóbal! Huh.

09:16.500 --> 09:19.000
<c.speaker>Elena's scepter.

09:19.000 --> 09:20.708
<c.speaker>Oh, there's my cousin.

09:20.708 --> 09:23.166
<c.speaker>Wait here. Cristóbal!

09:23.166 --> 09:24.333
<c.speaker>Elena?!

09:24.333 --> 09:25.500
<c.speaker>You found my scepter.

09:25.500 --> 09:27.208
<c.speaker>-Who did this?
-Shuriki.

09:27.208 --> 09:29.291
<c.speaker>But don't worry.
I'll stop her.

09:33.083 --> 09:34.583
<c.speaker>[gasp]

09:36.875 --> 09:38.166
<c.speaker>[laughing]

09:38.166 --> 09:40.000
<c.speaker>I have other plans.

09:40.000 --> 09:41.750
<c.speaker>-[gasp]
-Guards!

09:41.750 --> 09:43.208
<c.speaker>[gasp]

09:43.208 --> 09:45.208
<c.speaker>Cristóbal?
What are you doing?

09:45.208 --> 09:46.583
<c.speaker>Oh, It's simple, really.

09:46.583 --> 09:48.000
<c.speaker>When Shuriki ruled Avalor,

09:48.000 --> 09:51.291
<c.speaker>she gave me gold
in return for my loyalty.

09:51.291 --> 09:52.875
<c.speaker>But when you
got rid of her,

09:52.875 --> 09:55.875
<c.speaker>you also got rid
of my gold supply.

09:55.875 --> 09:59.291
<c.speaker>Now I have just one yacht,
and look at me,

09:59.291 --> 10:00.500
<c.speaker>practically wasting away.

10:02.083 --> 10:04.083
<c.speaker>Luckily for me,
Shuriki returned,

10:04.083 --> 10:07.250
<c.speaker>and together,
we hatched this lovely plan

10:07.250 --> 10:11.000
<c.speaker>to restore Avalor, and me,
to our former glory.

10:11.000 --> 10:14.708
<c.speaker>You betrayed
your own <i>familia </i>for gold?

10:14.708 --> 10:18.125
<c.speaker>"Betrayed" is
such a nasty word.

10:18.125 --> 10:21.250
<c.speaker>I prefer, mmm...

10:21.250 --> 10:23.083
<c.speaker>No, you're right.
"Betrayed" works.

10:23.083 --> 10:25.458
<c.speaker>And we are talking
about a lot of gold.

10:25.458 --> 10:26.875
<c.speaker>[snap]

10:26.875 --> 10:28.083
<c.speaker>-[grunts]
-[Marisa] Get away from her!

10:31.166 --> 10:32.833
<c.speaker>Let her go!

10:32.833 --> 10:33.958
<c.speaker>-Unh!
-[guards groan]

10:36.000 --> 10:38.333
<c.speaker>[both gasp]

10:38.333 --> 10:41.166
<c.speaker>Take Princess Elena
to the palace
for her own safety.

10:41.166 --> 10:43.083
<c.speaker>And lock up that sirena!

10:46.583 --> 10:47.958
<c.speaker>Marisa!

10:49.708 --> 10:51.000
<c.speaker>Marzel, you're outnumbered.

10:51.000 --> 10:53.000
<c.speaker>You'll just get
yourself caught, too.

10:53.000 --> 10:55.250
<c.speaker>We gotta go tell the king!

11:05.458 --> 11:07.333
<c.speaker>[Luna]
Princess Elena!

11:07.333 --> 11:08.708
<c.speaker>Cristóbal's with Shuriki!

11:08.708 --> 11:10.125
<c.speaker>He's taking us prisoner!

11:10.125 --> 11:11.333
<c.speaker>-What?!
-Prisoner?!

11:11.333 --> 11:13.166
<c.speaker>Not on my watch!

11:14.166 --> 11:16.375
<c.speaker>Oh! Get them!

11:16.375 --> 11:18.000
<c.speaker>No! Naomi!

11:18.000 --> 11:19.416
<c.speaker>[struggling]

11:19.416 --> 11:21.333
<c.speaker>-[Luna grunts]
-Whoa! Look out!

11:24.333 --> 11:27.166
<c.speaker>We need to find
Gabe and Mateo now!

11:29.708 --> 11:30.708
<c.speaker>[gasping]

11:30.708 --> 11:31.708
<c.speaker>Elena!

11:31.708 --> 11:33.208
<c.speaker>Shuriki's in the palace!

11:33.208 --> 11:35.083
<c.speaker>Of course she is.

11:35.083 --> 11:37.125
<c.speaker>Who do you think invited her?

11:37.125 --> 11:38.125
<c.speaker>[family gasping]

11:38.125 --> 11:39.291
<c.speaker>He's on her side.

11:39.291 --> 11:42.166
<c.speaker>-That scoundrel!
-What?!

11:42.166 --> 11:44.958
<c.speaker>So the Duke and Shuriki
are in this together?

11:44.958 --> 11:46.333
<c.speaker>We have to warn
the Royal Family.

11:46.333 --> 11:47.708
<c.speaker>They're back
at the palace.

11:47.708 --> 11:49.875
<c.speaker>Then it's up to us
to rescue them.

11:49.875 --> 11:52.125
<c.speaker>And I think I know
where to start looking.

11:54.833 --> 11:57.833
<c.speaker>Hmm.
The throne suits you.

11:57.833 --> 11:59.458
<c.speaker>Every throne does!

11:59.458 --> 12:01.875
<c.speaker>That's what
I was going to say.

12:01.875 --> 12:04.250
<c.speaker>Bravo! Bravo!

12:04.250 --> 12:07.833
<c.speaker>You did it!
You pulled it off!

12:07.833 --> 12:09.208
<c.speaker>Well, almost.

12:09.208 --> 12:10.708
<c.speaker>Almost?

12:10.708 --> 12:14.625
<c.speaker>Elena survived
your little surprise attack.

12:14.625 --> 12:16.083
<c.speaker>-What?!
-Not to worry.

12:16.083 --> 12:18.000
<c.speaker>I scooped her up.

12:18.000 --> 12:19.000
<c.speaker>Where is she?!

12:19.000 --> 12:21.166
<c.speaker>[grunting]

12:21.166 --> 12:22.125
<c.speaker>Ay, forget it, Elena!

12:22.125 --> 12:23.208
<c.speaker>It's useless!

12:23.208 --> 12:24.416
<c.speaker>There's no way
out of here!

12:24.416 --> 12:25.958
<c.speaker>-[crash]
-Aah!

12:27.875 --> 12:29.208
<c.speaker>You were saying?

12:29.208 --> 12:30.583
<c.speaker>What was that?

12:30.583 --> 12:33.000
<c.speaker>Intruders on the tower roof!

12:33.000 --> 12:34.208
<c.speaker>[growls]

12:35.333 --> 12:37.250
<c.speaker>Ohh!

12:37.250 --> 12:38.708
<c.speaker>Who's coming up first?

12:38.708 --> 12:41.250
<c.speaker>Ooh! Me! Me!

12:41.250 --> 12:43.583
<c.speaker>Ahem. Or Isabel.

12:43.583 --> 12:45.291
<c.speaker>Or both of you!

12:45.291 --> 12:46.291
<c.speaker><i>Llévaluq! </i>

12:49.750 --> 12:51.000
<c.speaker>Take them to the galleon.

12:51.000 --> 12:52.208
<c.speaker>Then come back
for the others.

12:52.208 --> 12:53.166
<c.speaker>Hold on tight!

13:00.250 --> 13:01.458
<c.speaker>They're coming! Hurry!

13:02.958 --> 13:04.125
<c.speaker>Demolish!

13:08.833 --> 13:11.458
<c.speaker>Oh! Summon my jaquins!

13:14.333 --> 13:15.875
<c.speaker>Faster, beast!

13:15.875 --> 13:17.708
<c.speaker>The name's Cruz.

13:18.875 --> 13:21.458
<c.speaker>[Isabel] Elena!

13:21.458 --> 13:22.458
<c.speaker>[gasp]

13:27.333 --> 13:30.125
<c.speaker>Esteban, get Isa
and our <i>abuelos </i>below deck!

13:30.125 --> 13:31.333
<c.speaker>But what about you?!

13:31.333 --> 13:33.000
<c.speaker>You do not
have your scepter!

13:35.625 --> 13:37.166
<c.speaker>Demolish!

13:37.166 --> 13:39.458
<c.speaker>-Incoming!
-Aah!

13:39.458 --> 13:42.708
<c.speaker>All of you,
down below! Now!

13:42.708 --> 13:43.708
<c.speaker><i>Vetzi! </i>

13:45.125 --> 13:47.250
<c.speaker>-Whoaaaaa!
-Aaaaah!

13:47.250 --> 13:48.291
<c.speaker>Stop spinning!

13:48.291 --> 13:51.416
<c.speaker>I'm tryin'!

13:51.416 --> 13:52.583
<c.speaker><i>Conglari! </i>

13:52.583 --> 13:53.583
<c.speaker>That's better!

13:53.583 --> 13:55.875
<c.speaker>-Whoa!
-Oh! Ohh!

13:55.875 --> 13:57.208
<c.speaker>[Shuriki and Fiero screaming]

13:58.625 --> 14:00.166
<c.speaker>[all groaning]

14:00.166 --> 14:01.958
<c.speaker>Oh!

14:01.958 --> 14:03.333
<c.speaker>[Shuriki grunting]

14:03.333 --> 14:04.625
<c.speaker>Oh!

14:04.625 --> 14:05.625
<c.speaker>Get up! Now!

14:05.625 --> 14:07.708
<c.speaker>[Vestia grunting]

14:09.416 --> 14:11.416
<c.speaker>-Quick! Toss me a crossbow!
-Unh!

14:14.375 --> 14:16.000
<c.speaker>Demolish!

14:16.000 --> 14:17.083
<c.speaker>Take cover!

14:18.708 --> 14:19.708
<c.speaker>Aah!

14:21.333 --> 14:22.333
<c.speaker><i>Ximocu! </i>

14:25.500 --> 14:27.333
<c.speaker>[laughs]
Nice spell.

14:29.208 --> 14:30.208
<c.speaker>Mom!

14:32.583 --> 14:35.291
<c.speaker>Enough.
It's me Shuriki wants.

14:35.291 --> 14:37.166
<c.speaker>I'm only putting
you all in danger.

14:37.166 --> 14:39.208
<c.speaker>-No!
-Wait! Stop!

14:45.583 --> 14:47.291
<c.speaker>Now's your chance,
Shuriki!

14:47.291 --> 14:48.500
<c.speaker>You have a clear shot!

14:48.500 --> 14:50.625
<c.speaker><i>Adiós, Elena. </i>

14:50.625 --> 14:52.291
<c.speaker>-Infern-oh!
-[thud]

14:55.208 --> 14:56.750
<c.speaker>Oh!

14:59.083 --> 15:00.083
<c.speaker>[gasp]

15:05.625 --> 15:07.000
<c.speaker>They came!

15:10.125 --> 15:11.875
<c.speaker>Elena!

15:11.875 --> 15:13.000
<c.speaker>-Catch!
-[gasp]

15:15.833 --> 15:17.291
<c.speaker>Thanks, Marzel!

15:20.250 --> 15:21.708
<c.speaker>You convinced Papá!

15:21.708 --> 15:23.625
<c.speaker>Wasn't hard, once
you got yourself captured.

15:24.875 --> 15:26.458
<c.speaker>Now come on.

15:26.458 --> 15:28.833
<c.speaker>We have one last ship
to crash.

15:28.833 --> 15:32.875
<c.speaker>[all singing siren song]

15:34.708 --> 15:36.708
<c.speaker>Ah! Oh, no!

15:36.708 --> 15:38.291
<c.speaker>Cover your ears!

15:43.750 --> 15:45.750
<c.speaker>No! Turn the wheel!

15:49.458 --> 15:51.458
<c.speaker>-[all screaming]
-[groans]

15:52.875 --> 15:54.583
<c.speaker>My yacht!

15:54.583 --> 15:56.250
<c.speaker>My palace!

15:58.166 --> 15:59.416
<c.speaker>-Go, beast!
-[growls]

16:00.708 --> 16:02.291
<c.speaker>What about us?!

16:02.291 --> 16:05.000
<c.speaker>We can barricade ourselves
inside the palace!

16:08.083 --> 16:09.458
<c.speaker>I'll deal with Shuriki.

16:09.458 --> 16:10.958
<c.speaker>Can you guys
handle the others?

16:10.958 --> 16:13.333
<c.speaker>Me and Gabe
against three malvagos?

16:13.333 --> 16:15.000
<c.speaker>I like our odds.

16:16.416 --> 16:18.166
<c.speaker>All right.
Let's get 'em.

16:25.250 --> 16:27.208
<c.speaker>[gasps]

16:31.000 --> 16:34.166
<c.speaker>We must stop meeting
like this, Elena.

16:34.166 --> 16:35.750
<c.speaker>Don't worry. We will.

16:35.750 --> 16:38.166
<c.speaker>-Glow!
-Demolis-- !

16:38.166 --> 16:39.875
<c.speaker>Blaze!

16:39.875 --> 16:41.208
<c.speaker>Whoa!

16:42.458 --> 16:43.750
<c.speaker><i>Vetzi! </i>

16:43.750 --> 16:45.583
<c.speaker>Did you guys
just hear something?

16:45.583 --> 16:46.708
<c.speaker>Oh!

16:46.708 --> 16:48.291
<c.speaker>-Whoa!
-Oof!

16:48.291 --> 16:50.000
<c.speaker>[grunting]

16:50.000 --> 16:52.250
<c.speaker>Oh! Unh! Oh! Ooh!

16:52.250 --> 16:53.708
<c.speaker>I've got Fiero.

16:55.583 --> 16:57.000
<c.speaker><i>Boqato! </i>

16:57.000 --> 16:58.208
<c.speaker><i>Ximocu! </i>

16:58.208 --> 16:59.750
<c.speaker>Ohh! [groans]

17:03.458 --> 17:04.625
<c.speaker>-Desp-- !
-[grunts]

17:06.083 --> 17:07.083
<c.speaker>[Carla]
<i>Ecatuul! </i>

17:09.083 --> 17:10.125
<c.speaker>Whoa!

17:11.125 --> 17:13.250
<c.speaker>Ha ha! Sorry.

17:14.833 --> 17:17.250
<c.speaker>"Sorry" is right!

17:17.250 --> 17:19.250
<c.speaker>-Where do you think
you're going?
-Whoa!

17:19.250 --> 17:21.208
<c.speaker>Wait! Let's make a deal.

17:21.208 --> 17:22.833
<c.speaker>I'll give you anything you want.

17:22.833 --> 17:25.083
<c.speaker>Nice try, fancy pants.

17:25.083 --> 17:26.083
<c.speaker>Whoa!

17:27.166 --> 17:28.583
<c.speaker><i>Boqato! </i>

17:28.583 --> 17:30.458
<c.speaker><i>Llévaluq! </i>

17:30.458 --> 17:32.000
<c.speaker>Unh!

17:32.000 --> 17:35.291
<c.speaker>[grunting]

17:35.291 --> 17:36.375
<c.speaker>-Yah!
-[groans]

17:39.708 --> 17:41.125
<c.speaker>Follow me, Carla! <i>Rápido! </i>

17:45.416 --> 17:46.625
<c.speaker><i>Poctaka! </i>

17:49.000 --> 17:50.000
<c.speaker>Ohh!

17:53.416 --> 17:55.250
<c.speaker>You've come
a long way, boy.

17:59.000 --> 18:00.291
<c.speaker>Mateo!

18:01.875 --> 18:03.000
<c.speaker><i>-Oncholoz! </i>
<i>-Vetzi! </i>

18:04.458 --> 18:06.250
<c.speaker><i>Meyazami! </i>

18:06.250 --> 18:07.333
<c.speaker>Huh!

18:09.958 --> 18:12.291
<c.speaker>Hmm. But not far enough.

18:12.291 --> 18:15.250
<c.speaker>Toss your tamborita to me
or say goodbye to your friend.

18:16.500 --> 18:18.333
<c.speaker>Uh...

18:18.333 --> 18:19.625
<c.speaker>Just blast him!

18:22.875 --> 18:25.458
<c.speaker>[laughing] Fool!

18:26.458 --> 18:27.708
<c.speaker>Ha!

18:27.708 --> 18:28.958
<c.speaker>[grunting]

18:28.958 --> 18:30.625
<c.speaker>Mateo!

18:30.625 --> 18:31.625
<c.speaker><i>Akatok! </i>

18:31.625 --> 18:34.000
<c.speaker><i>Congla-- Aah! </i>

18:40.333 --> 18:41.708
<c.speaker>Ya gotta admit,

18:41.708 --> 18:43.500
<c.speaker>he does make a good statue.

18:43.500 --> 18:46.125
<c.speaker>[gasp] Where are
Victor and Carla?

18:46.125 --> 18:48.291
<c.speaker>-They escaped.
-But not the Duke.

18:48.291 --> 18:50.125
<c.speaker>Oof!

18:50.125 --> 18:51.708
<c.speaker>[Shuriki] Demolish!

18:54.291 --> 18:57.166
<c.speaker>-Chaos!
-[Skylar] Whoa! Whoa! Whoa!

19:00.208 --> 19:01.500
<c.speaker>-Blaze!
-Ohh!

19:01.500 --> 19:02.583
<c.speaker>Inferno!

19:05.958 --> 19:08.083
<c.speaker>[Cruz] Whoa! That's it!
I'm outta here!

19:09.125 --> 19:10.125
<c.speaker>[Elena panting]

19:14.000 --> 19:15.083
<c.speaker>-[scepter buzzing]
-[gasp]

19:17.333 --> 19:19.416
<c.speaker>Still haven't mastered
your scepter?

19:19.416 --> 19:21.125
<c.speaker>Oh, how unfortunate.

19:21.125 --> 19:23.208
<c.speaker>When I'm done with you,

19:23.208 --> 19:26.583
<c.speaker>I'm going to finish off
what's left of your family.

19:26.583 --> 19:27.583
<c.speaker>[evil laugh]

19:29.208 --> 19:30.208
<c.speaker>Vanish!

19:32.166 --> 19:34.500
<c.speaker>Goodbye, Elena.

19:34.500 --> 19:36.125
<c.speaker>Demolish!

19:36.125 --> 19:37.208
<c.speaker>Vanish!

19:46.583 --> 19:47.583
<c.speaker>[Elena, whispering]
Missed me.

19:47.583 --> 19:48.583
<c.speaker>Wha-- ?

19:49.958 --> 19:51.208
<c.speaker>[gasp]

19:51.208 --> 19:52.333
<c.speaker>Blaze!

19:52.333 --> 19:53.583
<c.speaker>Oh! Ohh!

20:00.000 --> 20:02.000
<c.speaker>[groaning]

20:02.000 --> 20:03.250
<c.speaker>Unh!

20:06.958 --> 20:08.500
<c.speaker>Cruz... Bla--

20:08.500 --> 20:10.208
<c.speaker>[sigh]

20:10.208 --> 20:13.375
<c.speaker>-Princesa!
-He's-- He's getting away.

20:13.375 --> 20:16.208
<c.speaker>He doesn't matter.
You got Shuriki!

20:22.125 --> 20:24.083
<c.speaker>It's finally over.

20:28.750 --> 20:31.000
<c.speaker>[purring]

20:45.250 --> 20:46.708
<c.speaker>I don't know
what happened to them.

20:46.708 --> 20:48.291
<c.speaker>I say we make
a break for it.

20:48.291 --> 20:49.750
<c.speaker>[clink, orb rolling]

20:55.708 --> 20:58.500
<c.speaker>That is all
that's left of Shuriki.

21:00.625 --> 21:03.000
<c.speaker>That is more than enough.

21:03.000 --> 21:04.708
<c.speaker>[laughing]

21:04.708 --> 21:06.291
<c.speaker>Fly us out of here.

21:06.291 --> 21:08.291
<c.speaker>After you unfreeze
my sister.

21:09.125 --> 21:10.625
<c.speaker>[muffled shouts]

21:15.083 --> 21:18.458
<c.speaker>Shuriki is gone.
For good.

21:18.458 --> 21:19.875
<c.speaker>-Ay, <i>mija.  </i>
-You saved us all.

21:19.875 --> 21:21.458
<c.speaker>I was so worried.

21:22.583 --> 21:25.000
<c.speaker>You are sure this time?

21:25.000 --> 21:26.708
<c.speaker>I'm sure.

21:26.708 --> 21:28.208
<c.speaker>What do we do
with the Duke?

21:28.208 --> 21:30.458
<c.speaker>There's an empty cell
in the tower.

21:30.458 --> 21:31.583
<c.speaker>That'll do.

21:31.583 --> 21:34.583
<c.speaker>What? But I'm <i>familia! </i>

21:37.000 --> 21:40.083
<c.speaker>You have no idea
what that word means.

21:54.083 --> 21:57.708
<c.speaker>Let this be remembered
as the day sirenas and humans

21:57.708 --> 22:02.708
<c.speaker>defended Avalor together
and began a new era
of friendship!

22:05.750 --> 22:07.500
<c.speaker>You were right, <i>mija. </i>

22:07.500 --> 22:09.166
<c.speaker>This was our chance.

22:09.166 --> 22:11.000
<c.speaker>And I'm glad we took it.

22:15.625 --> 22:19.750
<c.speaker>Princess Elena, I look forward
to a new era of peace,

22:19.750 --> 22:21.500
<c.speaker>on land and sea.

22:22.875 --> 22:25.708
<c.speaker>[cheering]

22:25.708 --> 22:27.333
<c.speaker>Whoo-hoo!

22:27.333 --> 22:29.333
<c.speaker>[cheering]

22:34.083 --> 22:37.083
<c.speaker>I know. You told me so.

22:37.083 --> 22:38.083
<c.speaker>[chuckles]

22:45.375 --> 22:48.458
<c.speaker>I dreamt of this day
for so long.

22:48.458 --> 22:52.125
<c.speaker>Sometimes
dreams do come true.

23:03.583 --> 23:07.000
<c.speaker>[theme music playing]
